{"tid":1607661,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"到中午 12 點都無行動既話今日可以就咁算","createTime":"2019-10-01T02:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:02:35.000Z","uid":222614,"like":18,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fb29c542ba8bbbc7b8b09a889b888e8121cb08","tid":1607661,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"到中午 12 點都無行動既話，不如全日豪畀愛國團體，反正依家各區都有佢地啲活動，2000 架國旗的士周圍走<br />\n<br />\n大家可以等佢地散左，入夜先賀佢老母，橫掂大家都係夜行動物，夜晚應該會精神百倍"},{"pid":"0efc16c1183e35878f3ee30363e750ea7ad3f29b","tid":1607661,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"32407d07d6baaa0ba36ec5bd40a600ce7006746c","tid":1607661,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:29:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b6af2744df0b390e0e2eb5131012bf0c66216472","tid":1607661,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:30:24.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"8aef27c26344ea22498565942aa7264aa07510bb","tid":1607661,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花要對準政權，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=f3a2413c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=066b6908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=807099f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0440214d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=fd50b265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=43b143ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"5a071c116ab8000bd2c743f1639349574bb5c396","tid":1607661,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"不推文<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"7e1e05a5857fd268efba26fa2f0d1412f67a12d8","tid":1607661,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score